-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Tri%E1%BB%87u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-h%E1%BB%8Dc-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-NUZzpnYgJ9Giyx40vTdlVQ">Thứ vận Triệu đề học kiến ký - 次韻趙提學見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-s3x28VNwVFO_JS6LZ5Jo0w">Trần Hiến Chương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-H%E1%BA%A1c-Ni%C3%AAn/Tr%C3%BAc-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-zSJyGxARwhEPrlQCS8nE3A">Trúc chi từ kỳ 2 - 竹枝詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-H%E1%BA%A1c-Ni%C3%AAn/author-6o5MEWm8-MGYLu0WTNeA4Q">Đinh Hạc Niên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/Tu-T%C3%A2y-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%9Di/poem-GRNH9SS7MhDNhNNF3-MOJQ">Tu Tây phương thập nhị thời - 修西方十二時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-D3nlI_QzeVjknjQ7vGsW3w">Thiện Đạo đại sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-8/poem-lhlBXuDa4lVE7rh3_Q33Ww">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 8 - 絕句漫興其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
